Don't you forget that.

957
01:21:58,681 --> 01:22:00,681
I won't.

958
01:22:00,683 --> 01:22:03,951
Nor will I forget
he's a god of wrath.

959
01:22:16,364 --> 01:22:17,531
Mmm...

960
