01:27:44,525 --> 01:27:46,860
The battle's begun, ma.

987
01:27:47,895 --> 01:27:49,796
Simon.

988
01:27:53,334 --> 01:27:55,736
Simon will take you
to Reese's.

989
01:27:55,738 --> 01:27:57,638
