1029
01:32:38,186 --> 01:32:39,819
Tell the men to fall back.

1030
01:32:39,821 --> 01:32:41,555
What?

1031
01:32:41,557 --> 01:32:42,889
If we have a gun battle now,

1032
01:32:42,891 --> 01:32:44,090
